{"tid":368671,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[中秋佳節] 冰皮月餅vs傳統月餅","createTime":"2017-08-21T17:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:47:33.000Z","uid":129039,"like":78,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8a535a0a24a76a84236c8255345b80d9c48700","tid":368671,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"冰皮月餅，好多種味道，綠豆、蛋黄、藍莓、夏威夷果仁、芝麻、奶黃、楊枝甘露、朱古力、抺茶紅豆、芒果，多數用水果蓉做餡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/005245_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F005245_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e5f54393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/005251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F005251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5270897b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/005037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F005037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b1c21b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統月餅，例如雙黃白蓮蓉、純白蓮蓉、金華火腿、五仁月餅，深受老一輩歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/010156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F010156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4faf9a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/010159_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F010159_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9722ffdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2選1你會揀邊樣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:冰皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:傳統"},{"pid":"e4598bb452a7f577e803bfb364c754b323535b1c","tid":368671,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"卑鄙月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3a26027484c77b9729602cfa768ae0017514af","tid":368671,"uid":127770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"傳統走黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bfbd0c51469af3cd002d33c818b4fe26bf2853","tid":368671,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卑鄙月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊忽卑鄙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda4935611b0126ac14ba6dd72f3cba4e8b51b30","tid":368671,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳統走黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純蓮蓉?<br />\n會唔會好甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc3130e2224768d09313b69acfb6f1d029c1198","tid":368671,"uid":129039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"細個好鍾意食月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人多數買傳統月餅 雙黃白蓮蓉<br />\n我會將件月餅切開 搵嗰兩粒鹹蛋黃出嚟<br />\n再切四份或者兩份<br />\n拎有完整鹹蛋黃嗰份出嚟食<br />\n然後食層皮 再食晒啲蓮蓉<br />\n最尾食淨粒鹹蛋黃 慢慢嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582e1e6f884d9354bc7399